title: Windows 10 Home + Pro X64 Multilanguage Oct 2015 {Generation2}
description:
* Windows 10 Home + Pro X64 Multilanguage Oct 2015 {Generation2}


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one ISO [SOURCE ISO] and thirteen executable svf-files.

* All exe-files are created from Microsoft Updated RTM Build 10240,
* 10240 ESD 10240.16393.150909-1450 (released 9/20/2015)

* Info-link: 
[url]http://www.windowsnews.in/2015/09/microsoft-updates-rtm-build-10240-with.html[/url]

* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source)
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference.

* Hashes attached in a separate .txt

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ]

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language.exe

* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO

* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract the ORIGINAL ISO in the selected language.

[ CONTENTS ]

[ SOURCE ISO ]

* Win10.X64.en-US.iso - 4,48GB

* Pre-installed by Microsoft:
* KB3081452 
* KB3081455

* Integrated / Pre-installed in audit mode:

* .NET Framework 3.5
* KB3081449
* KB3087040
* KB3097617
* KB3099406
* KB3074678
* KB3074686

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]
